article.description: — Bryce Hamilton had 18 points and eight rebounds as UNLV topped San Jose State 76-60 on Friday night.
article.headline: Hamilton scores 18 to carry UNLV over San Jose St. 76-60
article.linkText: Hamilton scores 18 to carry UNLV over San Jose St. 76-60
article.story: SAN JOSE, Calif. -- — Bryce Hamilton had 18 points and eight rebounds as UNLV topped San Jose State 76-60 on Friday night. David Jenkins Jr. had 16 points for UNLV (9-11, 6-7 Mountain West Conference), which broke its six-game road losing streak. Devin Tillis added 14 points. Moses Wood had 11 points. Ralph Agee had 18 points for the Spartans (5-14, 3-12). Trey Smith added 15 points.
